{"title": "RustScan", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "rustscan", "html": "<h1 id=\"rustscan\">RustScan</h1>\n<h2 id=\"basic-usage\">Basic Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Default scan (all ports)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Single port</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;port&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple ports</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">22</span>,80,443,445\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Port range</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>-65535\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Scan multiple hosts</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;,192.168.1.2,192.168.1.3\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Scan CIDR range</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Scan from file</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--addresses-from-file<span class=\"w\"> </span>targets.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"speed-tuning\">Speed Tuning</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Increase ulimit for more open file descriptors (critical for speed)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">ulimit</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Batch size (number of ports scanned per round)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Timeout per port (ms)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1500</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Max combined: fastest possible</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Conservative for unstable targets</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">500</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">500</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3000</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTB/CTF standard</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"pipe-to-nmap\">Pipe to Nmap</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Pass discovered ports directly to nmap (default behavior with --)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full service/version + scripts</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oN<span class=\"w\"> </span>nmap_output.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Vuln scripts via nmap</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"o\">=</span>vuln\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># OS detection</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-O<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom nmap flags</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version-intensity<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">9</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>scan_&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No ping + nmap</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-Pn<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/scan_&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Domain controller recon</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/dc_&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"scanning-ranges\">Scanning Ranges</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># /24 subnet</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.1.0/24<span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple ranges</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.10.0/24,10.10.11.0/24\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># /16 (slower, use with care)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.0.0/16<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">500</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3000</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"specific-port-patterns\">Specific Port Patterns</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Web ports only</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">80</span>,443,8000,8080,8443,8888,9090\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Windows common ports</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span>,22,23,25,53,80,88,135,139,389,443,445,464,593,636,1433,3268,3269,3389,5985,9389\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Linux common ports</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">21</span>,22,25,53,80,110,111,143,443,445,2049,3306,5432,6379,8080,8443,27017\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTB all ports fast</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">65535</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>-65535\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"output-options\">Output Options</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Output to file</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># JSON output</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--output-format<span class=\"w\"> </span>json<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.json\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># JSON via greppable</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--greppable\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Quiet (only ports, no banner)</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-q\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No banner</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--no-config\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"common-usage-patterns\">Common Usage Patterns</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># HTB/CTF one-liner: fast discovery + nmap service scan</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/scan_&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Stealth: slow batch to avoid rate limiting</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Network range host discovery then port scan</span>\nrustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.10.10.0/24<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">500</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sV<span class=\"w\"> </span>--open\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full pipeline: rustscan ports -&gt; nmap deep dive</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">ports</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>rustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-q<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>&gt;/dev/null<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Open&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>awk<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{print $2}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>cut<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"s1\">&#39;:&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f2<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>tr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\n&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;,&#39;</span><span class=\"k\">)</span>\nnmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">$ports</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/deep_&lt;ip&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Wrapper function for HTB workflow</span>\nhtbscan<span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span>rustscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">$1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ulimit<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--<span class=\"w\"> </span>-sCV<span class=\"w\"> </span>-Pn<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/htb_<span class=\"nv\">$1</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\nhtbscan<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "RustScan Basic Usage # Default scan (all ports) rustscan -a &lt;ip&gt; # Single port rustscan -a &lt;ip&gt; -p &lt;port&gt; # Multiple ports rustscan -a &lt;ip&gt; -p 22 ,80,443,445 # Port range rusts", "tags": []}